CREATE TABLE Celebrities (
	id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
	name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
	age INT NOT NULL,
	nationality VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
)
CREATE TABLE celebrities (id INT, name VARCHAR(255), nationality VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE movies (id INT, title VARCHAR(255), release_date DATE);
CREATE TABLE awards (id INT, celebrity_id INT, award_name VARCHAR(255), year INT);

CREATE TABLE celebrities (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name STRING,
  age INT,
  nationality STRING);

CREATE TABLE movies (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  title STRING,
  release_date DATE,
  genre STRING,
  celebrity_id INT REFERENCES celebrities(id));

CREATE TABLE awards (id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name STRING,
  category STRING,
  year INT,
  celebrity_id INT REFERENCES celebrities(id));

CREATE TABLE Movies (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  title VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL,
  release_year INTEGER,
  director VARCHAR(100),
  nationality VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Awards (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  category VARCHAR(100),
  year INTEGER,
  celebrity_id INTEGER,
  FOREIGN KEY (celebrity_id) REFERENCES Celebrities(id)
);

CREATE TABLE Songs (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  title VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL,
  artist VARCHAR(100),
  release_year INTEGER,
  nationality VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Books (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  title VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL,
  author VARCHAR(100),
  publish_year INTEGER,
  nationality VARCHAR(50)
);
